      "name": "Decision Trace Reconstructor",
      "description": "Reference implementation of the Decision Evidence Maturity Model (DEMM) property-level reconstructability assessment. Post-hoc reconstruction of multi-step decision chains from fragmentary evidence with decision-event schema mapping and authorization-envelope substitution for ML-opaque steps.",
